{
  "title": "Fluffy Spanish Almonds Torta",
  "description": "A fresh and fluffy Spanish-inspired dish featuring almond extract and score-fat, perfect for a low-carb friendly sick-day meal. This torta is a twist on traditional Spanish cuisine, ideal for breakfast, lunch, or a mid-afternoon snack.",
